OL,3,CInvestigation launched after fire
OL,4,Cbreaks out at scrap metal yard
OL,6,FAn investigation has been launched
OL,7,Fafter a fire broke out at a scrap
OL,8,Fmetal yard in Bristol overnight.
OL,10,FCrews were called to Deep Pit Road in
OL,11,FSpeedwell at 11:15pm on Sunday (12th
OL,12,FApril).
OL,14,FEmergency teams from Kingswood, Hicks
OL,15,FGate, Bath, Bedminster, Portishead,
OL,16,FTemple, Yate and Weston-super-Mare
OL,17,Fattended.
OL,19,FUpon arrival, firefighters found a
OL,20,Flarge blaze within a building, which
OL,21,Fwas eventually extinguished.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
