OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1776265866
OL,3,CInvestigation launched after fire
OL,4,Cbreaks out at scrap metal yard
OL,6,F11 firefighters used breathing
OL,7,Fapparatus, a turntable ladder and 4
OL,8,Fwater jets.
OL,10,FSeveral fire engines were still on the
OL,11,Fscene this morning, checking for
OL,12,Fhotspots with thermal imaging cameras.
OL,14,FAvon Fire and Rescue Service has
OL,15,Fconfirmed there were no casualties in
OL,16,Fthe incident.
OL,18,FThe cause of the fire is unknown, but
OL,19,Fan investigation is underway.
